prefuse.visual
Interface DecoratorItem

All Superinterfaces:
Tuple, VisualItem
All Known Implementing Classes:
TableDecoratorItem
public interface DecoratorItem
extends VisualItem

VisualItem that "decorates" another VisualItem. DecoratorItem instances allow the decorated item to be retrieved, and used to compute visual properties for this item. Example decorator items might include attaching an external label to an item or adding interactive handles to another item.

Author:
jeffrey heer
